{"tid":1437382,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"視后田蕊妮慘成內地網民狙擊新目標　受盡謾罵：麻煩封殺","createTime":"2019-08-09T13:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:59:34.000Z","uid":68738,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c2953b44fb2d6b90c620d10057de868ca3bf44e","tid":1437382,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3133007/org/979ef23452d2267fc2dc09e64ceb691e.jpg/hC15m6SuHKXpbsyxYHNsVavj4QHbJ2Lz5lC-EuZQvhI?v=w960r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3133007%2Forg%2F979ef23452d2267fc2dc09e64ceb691e.jpg%2FhC15m6SuHKXpbsyxYHNsVavj4QHbJ2Lz5lC-EuZQvhI%3Fv%3Dw960r16_9&h=ff2836e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現年41歲的田蕊妮向來甚少談政治，但在前日（5日）就罕有地在Facebook留言：「我依家開個記者會宣布一陣間會有一個記者會，嗰個記者會嘅內容係聽日會有一個記者會⋯⋯⋯」，疑似不滿林鄭記招「無限Loop」。此Post一出，即引起不少內地網民熱議，更有網民質疑田蕊妮老公在香港鬧事的同時，她昨日還在內地登台搵真銀。但事實上，網民說的所謂「昨日登台」，其實已經是去年10月在成都的活動。<br />\n<br />\n目前，不少內地網民仍然在微博留言攻擊田蕊妮，更聲稱要將她全面封殺！而田蕊妮所主演的TVB新劇《她。她。她的少女時代》將於本月19日播出，之後她又會在9月20日於旺角麥花臣場館再度舉行個人演唱會，未知會否受到事件影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/361168/%E8%A6%96%E5%90%8E%E7%94%B0%E8%95%8A%E5%A6%AE%E6%85%98%E6%88%90%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99-%E5%8F%97%E7%9B%A1%E8%AC%BE%E7%BD%B5-%E9%BA%BB%E7%85%A9%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F361168%2F%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2590%258E%25E7%2594%25B0%25E8%2595%258A%25E5%25A6%25AE%25E6%2585%2598%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%258B%2599%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%25A8%2599-%25E5%258F%2597%25E7%259B%25A1%25E8%25AC%25BE%25E7%25BD%25B5-%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E7%2585%25A9%25E5%25B0%2581%25E6%25AE%25BA%3Futm_medium%3DSocia